      "content": "wait 600mg every 6 hours?? that sounds like a lot. and why do i need to be fasting for 8 hours before taking it? i just want the headache to stop so i can sleep. is there any specific reason i should be careful with the warfarin, or is it fine as long as i take the water like you said?",
